item.title: Pimpscape source
item.dc:creator: @Dell Dell
item.description:
@Dell wrote:

right click on runserver.bat, and rename it “Run&Compile By Dell”, then right click it again and click edit.

A notepad will popup erase everything in it and paste this in there…

@echo off COLOR 09 title Dellscape Source "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\java" server pause

change the “06” to the “06” to the type of java you have…
